{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 46477091, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "EUBA-EFSA-2023-ENREL-01", "title": "Selection of hosting sites and fellows for EU-FORA (European Food Risk Assessment) Fellowship Programme", "publicationDateLong": 1699315200000, "callIdentifier": "EUBA-EFSA-2023-ENREL-01", "callTitle": "Selection of hosting sites and fellows for EU-FORA (European Food Risk Assessment) Fellowship Programme", "callccm2Id": 46477097, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 45532249, "abbreviation": "EUBA", "description": "EU Bodies and Agencies"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 45532245, "abbreviation": "EFSA", "description": "EFSA"}], "topicMGAs": [], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "EUBA EUBA Type of Action", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 45530684, "abbreviation": "EUBA", "description": "EUBA Type of MGA"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "07 November 2023", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["26 March 2024"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3510299": [{"action": "EUBA-EFSA-2023-ENREL-01 - EUBA EUBA Type of Action", "plannedOpeningDate": "07 November 2023", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["26 March 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 825000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2024"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Objective</SPAN>:<p>The European Food Risk Assessment Fellowship (EU-FORA) Programme was established to help achieve one of EFSA\u2019s strategic objectives: Strengthening the food risk assessment capacity (including animal health and plant health) and knowledge community across Europe. The EU-FORA programme will establish a regular 12-month learning-by-doing fellowship, the objectives of which are to attract and motivate mid-career professionals to become risk assessors, thus increasing the pool of experts available in Europe; intensify exchange and cooperation among national food safety agencies and EFSA, hence stimulating the involvement of MS in regulatory risk assessment work; contribute to harmonising and further developing food safety risk assessment practices and methodologies across Europe, with the aim of building a common EU culture for risk assessment.</p>\n", "conditions": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:#404040;background:white\">1. Eligibility criteria: as described in section 2.2 of the call for proposals document <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:#404040;background:white\">2. Exclusion criteria: as described in section 2.3 of the call for proposals document <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:#404040;background:white\">3. Financial capacity: as described in section 2.4A of the call for proposals document <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:#404040;background:white\">4. Operational capacity: as described in section 2.4B of the call for proposals document <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;color:#404040;background:white\">5. Award criteria:<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>as described in section 2.5 of the call for proposals document <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div><font color=\"#404040\" face=\"Arial\" size=\"2\"><b><br />\r\n</b></font></div>\n<p class